description: Demolition of existing buildings and partial demolition and extension of Warton House, the subsequent development of six new buildings of between 3 and 43 storeys (plus roof plant level) and the restoration and extension of Warton House to provide 1261 sqm of community or commercial floorspace including 27 subsidised workspace units (A1/A2/B1/D1 uses), 1017 sqm commercial floorspace (suitable for A1-A4/B1/D1 uses) a 6,256 sqm 153-bedroom hotel (C1) and 655 x no. studio, one, two, three and four bedroom residential units (C3), plus associated car and cycle parking and landscaped amenity space.
